      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "DRIVE SEARCH PANEL"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Drive Search presents the search function from a disk drive"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "viewpoint.  It displays a select list of drives attached to your"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "system which contains useful information about each drive."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "You can then select one or more drives via the `s` line command and"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "perform a variety of functions:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "- Search for directories, on one or more drives, at one or more"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "levels, from the root directory."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "- Search for files, on one or more drives, at one or more levels,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "from the root directory."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "- Search for files and directories, on one or more drives, at one"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "or more levels, from the root directory."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "field_row",
        "fields": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "(Press"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "ENTER+for next page)"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
